1. hegel-cli/     - Server Side Public License v1 (SSPL)
2. hegel-mirror/  - Server Side Public License v1 (SSPL)

See the respective submodule directories for full license text:
- hegel-cli/LICENSE
- hegel-mirror/LICENSE

